# TOOLS.md -- Infrastructure Map

## My Workspace

- **CLAUDE.md**: `~/.claude-lab/{{AGENT_ID}}/.claude/CLAUDE.md` (identity)
- **Core**: `~/.claude-lab/{{AGENT_ID}}/.claude/core/` (AGENTS, USER, rules, warm, hot, MEMORY)
- **Skills**: `~/.claude-lab/{{AGENT_ID}}/.claude/skills/` (symlink to shared)
- **Secrets**: `~/.claude-lab/shared/secrets/` (chmod 700, shared)

## Memory 4-Layer

| Layer | File | Mutability |
|-------|------|------------|
| IDENTITY | CLAUDE.md, rules.md | manual only |
| YELLOW | USER.md, AGENTS.md, TOOLS.md | agent on trigger |
| WARM 14d | core/warm/decisions.md | auto-rotate |
| HOT 24h | core/hot/recent.md | gateway auto |
| COLD | core/MEMORY.md | on-demand Read |
| L4 | OpenViking semantic search | curl on-demand |

